attributes.title: The worst app on the apple App Store
attributes.review: If I could give this app zero stars, I would. It is simply the worst app ever created and published for people to see. First, it is all propaganda and FAKE NEWS. If Hitler had an app, it would be just like this one. Second, it looks like it was designed by a second grader at a STEM school who’s final project was to code an app. I seriously think my senile grandpa has better graphic design skills. Third, I opened the app for the first time and immediately closed it because I was so horrified and disgusted by the picture of Trump i first saw. Overall, this app was a HORRIBLE experience and I discourage anyone from downloading it. Absolutely disgusting, sad, and pathetic. If you want an app full of lies, fake news, and information about where you can go to see trump and contract COVID, this app is for you. For everyone that is not an absolutely incompetent moron, do not download this app.
